data.title: Siavibe Music
data.meta_description:
The Alibiez by Style MiSia, released 13 September 2019

1. The Move - Intro
2. Saturation
3. The Promise
4. Funky Fresh (Interlude)
5. Its All Your Fault
6. The Human Eye
7. Lurkin' (Interlude)
8. Too Many Questions
9. Origins Of Self
10. No Need To Search
11. Love, Devotion, Surrender
12. Plug Tunin' (Interlude)
13. Origins Of Self -Slow Mobb Remix
14. I Still Got Tomorrow
15. Off Tha Head Fo' 99
16. Dedication
17. What I Got
18. Love is Real (Interlude)
19. Adia (True Romance)
20. Electric Love (Interlude)
21. Escape Artists 98' (Feat. Scarub of Living Legends)
22. Sayonara

This is the 2nd Solo Emcee album from Style MiSia of Daysmen Empire that was released in 1999. These songs were recorded on analog and digital 4-track between 1997-1999. All Produced, composed, arranged by Style MiSia. Re-Released digitally on all streaming platforms 9/13/2019. The only Emcee feature on here is Scarub of Living Legends for the Bandcamp version, it is not on the DSP release version.
